manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "timothe-rs"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "timothe-rs"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.66"
bytes = "1.2.1"
chrono-tz = "0.6.3"
dirs = "4.0.0"
futures = "0.3.25"
futures-util = "0.3.24"
humantime = "2.1.0"
log = "0.4.17"
poise = "0.3.0"
pretty_env_logger = "0.4.0"
regex = "1.6.0"
saffron = "0.1.0"
shellexpand = "2.1.2"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.12"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.config]
version = "0.13.2"
features = ["toml"]

[dependencies.ical]
version = "0.7.*"
features = ["ical", "vcard"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.postcard]
version = "1.0.0"
features = ["alloc"]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.12"
features = ["rustls-tls"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.147"
features = ["rc"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.21.2"
features = ["full"]
